data.description: Beautiful, modern, large move-in-ready home in Somerton's NEWEST subdivision! This gem is just a year old and owners spared no expense to make this one a show stopper. With 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, a fully landscaped backyard, wood-like tile in various areas, water system, and many many more upgrades, WHY WOULD YOU WAIT TO BUILD WHEN YOU CAN HAVE THIS ONE! Call to schedule a showing TODAY.
